data.comment: The whistle has gone to start the match.
Throw-in for Cerezo at Yanmar Stadium Nagai.
In the minute 4, Tokyo have been awarded a corner by Yudai Yamamoto.
Tokyo's Yojiro Takahagi is on target but unsuccessful.
Tokyo are caught offside.
In the minute 5, Yudai Yamamoto awards the away team a throw-in.
In Osaka, Cerezo push forward quickly but are pulled up for offside.
Corner awarded to Cerezo.
In the minute 9, Throw-in Tokyo.
Cerezo awarded a free kick in their own half.
Cerezo drives forward and Tatsuhiro Sakamoto gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
In the minute 12, Corner awarded to Cerezo.
Free kick for Tokyo in their own half.
Cerezo needs to be cautious. Tokyo have an attacking throw-in.
In the minute 13, Ball safe as Cerezo is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Yudai Yamamoto signals a free kick to Cerezo in their own half.
Yudai Yamamoto signals a free kick to Tokyo in their own half.
In the minute 15, Free kick Tokyo.
In Osaka Tokyo attack through Diego Oliveira. The finish is off target, however.
Ball goes out of play for a Cerezo goal kick.
In the minute 16, Yudai Yamamoto signals a Tokyo throw-in in Cerezo's half.
Throw-in for Cerezo close to the penalty box.
Free kick for Cerezo in their own half.
In the minute 19, Cerezo are in shooting range from this free kick.
Tokyo have been awarded a corner by Yudai Yamamoto.
Naoyuki Fujita for Cerezo gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
In the minute 23, It's a goal kick for the away team in Osaka.
Cerezo awarded a free kick in their own half.
Diego Oliveira gets his shot on target but fails to score for Tokyo.
In the minute 30, Cerezo awarded a free kick in their own half.
Cerezo have a dangerous throw-in.
Tokyo awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 32, Free kick for Tokyo in their own half.
Can Tokyo get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Cerezo's half?
Tokyo are too eager and fall into an offside trap.
In the minute 38, Throw-in for Cerezo in their own half.
Yudai Yamamoto signals a free kick to Tokyo.
At Yanmar Stadium Nagai, Bruno Pereira Mendes has been yellow-carded for the home team.
In the minute 40, Diego Oliveira (Tokyo) is first to the ball but his header is off-target.
Cerezo have a goal kick.
Yudai Yamamoto signals a free kick to Cerezo in their own half.
In the minute 43, Corner awarded to Cerezo.
Yudai Yamamoto signals a free kick to Tokyo in their own half.
Tokyo drive upfield and Shuto Abe gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Cerezo defender.
In the minute 45, Tokyo have been awarded a corner by Yudai Yamamoto.
In Osaka, Masato Morishige (Tokyo) misses the target with a header.
Yudai Yamamoto awards Cerezo a goal kick.
In the minute 45, 3 minutes will be added to the 1st half.
Free kick for Tokyo in their own half.
The first-half is over at Yanmar Stadium Nagai.
In the minute 46, The second-half is now underway.
In Osaka Cerezo drive forward through Tatsuhiro Sakamoto. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Corner awarded to Tokyo.
In the minute 50, Can Cerezo capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Tokyo's half?
Throw-in high up the field for Tokyo in Osaka.
Cerezo awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 53, Ken Tokura is on a sub for Bruno Pereira Mendes for Cerezo.
Cerezo's Hiroshi Kiyotake gets in a shot on goal at Yanmar Stadium Nagai. But the effort is unsuccessful.
Yudai Yamamoto signals a throw-in for Tokyo, close to Cerezo's area.
In the minute 55, Tokyo needs to be cautious. Cerezo have an attacking throw-in.
Tokyo will need to be alert as they defend a dangerous free kick from Cerezo.
Goal kick for Tokyo at Yanmar Stadium Nagai.
Throw-in for Cerezo in their own half.
In the minute 57, Takuya Uchida is replacing Kensuke Nagai for the away team.
Free kick for Cerezo in the half of Tokyo.
In the minute 59, Yudai Yamamoto signals a throw-in for Cerezo, close to Tokyo's area.
Throw-in Tokyo.
Yudai Yamamoto waits before resuming play because Tsuyoshi Watanabe for Tokyo is still down.
In the minute 65, Hiroaki Okuno of Cerezo smashes in a shot on target. The keeper saves, though.
Tokyo have been awarded a corner by Yudai Yamamoto.
Tokyoâ€™s Tsuyoshi Watanabe is on his feet again at Yanmar Stadium Nagai.
In the minute 67, Arthur Silva for Tokyo drives towards goal at Yanmar Stadium Nagai. But the finish is unsuccessful.
Throw-in for Tokyo at Yanmar Stadium Nagai.
Tokyo to take a throw-in in Cerezo territory.
In the minute 70, Cerezo drive forward at breakneck speed but are pulled up for offside.
Yudai Yamamoto awards the home team a throw-in.
Tokyo push forward at Yanmar Stadium Nagai and Diego Oliveira gets in a strike. This is blocked, however, by a determined Cerezo defence.
In the minute 72, Cerezo awarded a free kick in their own half.
Free kick for Tokyo in their own half.
Leandro Desabato (Cerezo) has received a first yellow card.
In the minute 74, Yudai Yamamoto signals a free kick to Cerezo in their own half.
Takuya Uchida of Tokyo gets in a strike, but is off target.
Cerezo have a goal kick.
In the minute 75, Tokyo push upfield but Yudai Yamamoto quickly pulls them for offside.
Yusuke Maruhashi (Cerezo) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Throw-in for Cerezo close to the penalty box.
In the minute 78, Yudai Yamamoto signals a free kick to Cerezo in their own half.
Shuto Abe (Tokyo) has received a yellow card from Yudai Yamamoto.
The home team have replaced Hiroshi Kiyotake with Eiichi Katayama. This is the second substitution made today by Miguel Angel Lotina.
In the minute 79, Can Cerezo capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Tokyo's half?
It's a goal kick for the away team in Osaka.
Throw-in for Cerezo in the half of Tokyo.
In the minute 81, Yudai Yamamoto awards Tokyo a goal kick.
Tokyo make their second substitution with Taichi Hara replacing Arthur Silva.
Kenta Hasegawa (Tokyo) is making a third substitution, with Adailton replacing Diego Oliveira.
In the minute 83, Tokyo awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Corner awarded to Tokyo.
Tokyo's Shuto Abe gets his shot away but it misses the target.
In the minute 85, Goal kick for Cerezo at Yanmar Stadium Nagai.
In Osaka a free kick has been awarded the home team.
In the minute 86, In Osaka, Adailton of Tokyo is presented with a shooting opportunity. But the strike is blocked by the covering defence.
The home team replace Hiroaki Okuno with Toshiyuki Takagi.
Free kick for Cerezo in their own half.
Tokyo's Ryoya Ogawa has been booked in Osaka.
In the minute 88, Ball safe as Cerezo is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Ball goes out of play for a Tokyo goal kick.
In the minute 89, Throw-in Cerezo.
Kenta Hasegawa is making the team's fourth substitution at Yanmar Stadium Nagai with Hirotaka Mita replacing Shuto Abe.
Tokyo awarded a free kick in their own half.
4 minutes will be added to the 2nd half in Osaka.
Free kick for Cerezo in their own half.
Cerezo have a dangerous throw-in.
Tokyo push forward at Yanmar Stadium Nagai and Leandro gets in a great header. The attempt is cleared by the Cerezo defence.
Tokyo have been awarded a corner by Yudai Yamamoto.
A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Free kick Cerezo.
Full-time! The final score is 0-0.
